<h1>Welcome to Happy Feathers Hospital and Rehabilitation's (HFHR) official Patient Records Database Website! Above listed are our pages to interact with our database.</h1>
<h2>Our page is currently under construction, so while we lack functionality, heres an overview of what each page will have to offer soon!</h2>
<ul>
    <li><strong>View Birds:</strong> View all bird patients currently admitted to HFHR.</li>
    <li><strong>Add Bird:</strong> Add a new bird patient to the HFHR database.</li>
    <li><strong>Update Birds:</strong> Update information on existing bird patients.</li>
    <li><strong>View Species:</strong> View all bird species recognized by HFHR.</li>
    <li><strong>Add Species:</strong> Add a new bird species to the HFHR database.</li>
    <li><strong>Update Species:</strong> Update information on existing bird species.</li>
    <li><strong>View Owners:</strong> View all registered bird owners.</li>
    <li><strong>Add Owner:</strong> Add a new bird owner to the HFHR database.</li>
    <li><strong>Update Owners:</strong> Update information on existing bird owners.</li>
    <li><strong>View Feeds:</strong> View all types of bird feeds available at HFHR.</li>
    <li><strong>Add Feed:</strong> Add a new type of bird feed to the HFHR database.</li>
    <li><strong>Update Feeds:</strong> Update information on existing bird feeds.</li>
    <li><strong>View Feeding Logs:</strong> View all feeding log entries for bird patients.</li>
    <li><strong>Add Feeding Log Entry:</strong> Add a new feeding log entry for a bird patient.</li>
    <li><strong>Update Feeding Log Entry:</strong> Update information on existing feeding log entries.</li>
</ul>